1. *Kler* je dobrovoljno preuzeo ulogu vođe obnove crkve. (The clergyman voluntarily took up the role of leader of the church's restoration.)

2. Oni su se smatrali *klerom* nove religije. (They considered themselves the clergy of the new religion.)

3. *Klera* je bilo mnogo na misi. (There were many clergy at the mass.)

4. *Klerom* se smatraju ljudi koji su posvećeni služenju bogu. (Clergymen are considered people dedicated to serving God.)

5. *Kleru* su činili sveštenici, monasi i đakoni. (The clergy consisted of priests, monks and deacons.)